description: Finally winter has come to the Czech Republic. I was looking forward to a proper winter fuck. When I was walking by an ice skating rink I noticed there were some young guys. I didn´t hesitate, borrowed a pair of ice skates, and moved in. After first unsure steps I met a group of three boys, some of them were beginners like me. We had a lot of fun together. I almost forgot about my mission. When the time was right I went after the cutest one of them. He was originally from Bulgaria, which created a little language barrier but we managed. The boy was adorable, he had such a cute shy smile. I took him to the restroom to have some fun. It wasn´t easy because of all those people, still he gave me a pretty good blowjob.
title: Czech Hunter 283
